    "description": {
      "value": "<blockquote><p>Prerequisite: Level 12+ Warlock, Pact of the Chain invocation</p></blockquote><p>You can bind a creature that you can see within 60 feet in magical chains of force as a Magic action. When you do so, the target must make a Strength saving throw against your spell DC, If they fail, they are &amp;Reference[restrained].</p><p>On their turn they may use their action to attempt to free themselves from the chains by making a Strength saving throw. The chains disappear when the creature breaks free, after one minute has passed, or when you use Chains of Carceri again.</p><p><strong>Beam Replacement.</strong> This may be invoked in place of one of your Eldritch Blast beams.</p>",
